eventCard.title: Website Published!
eventCard.desc: The WSHS student council website has been published to the web! Check out all of the cool features on this article...

7467b8d0cbc3467dae2ad8a75a4d9094.source:
The website has been posted on the interet today! All announcements for and from Student Council will be posted on this site!

Here is a list of cool features to try out!

  • Check out our social media accounts at the bottom of the page!
  • Go to about page here to check out how this website was built
  • Look at more events that are coming up soon!
  • Send a rating on the contact page (All types of feedback are appriciated!!!)

If you would like to get in contact with Student Council: Please go to this page

Thanks for reading!
7467b8d0cbc3467dae2ad8a75a4d9094.author: Student Council

eventCard.title: Homecoming 2022
eventCard.desc: The Homecoming dance is coming up soon! Be sure to buy your tickets in B or C lunch 9-12 graders!

bf8d462207ae4005bcfd779a22716a18.source:
The Homecoming Dance is coming up soon!

The dance will take place on Sept. 24 from 7pm-10pm in the WSHS cafeteria.

Make sure to do a few things to get ready for the dance:

  • Buy your tickets for $10 during B and C lunches.
  • Only 9th-12th graders are able to attend the dance (if an student not at West Shamokin and under 21 would like to attend with their date, contact Mrs. Breznican)

Voting will be posted soon on the website so look out for updates!

If you would like to get in contact with Student Council: Please go to this page

Thanks for reading!
bf8d462207ae4005bcfd779a22716a18.author: Senior High STUCO
